                <span>Smart routing configuration</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <i
                  class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-accent mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"
                ></i>
                <span>Compliance & PCI setup</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <i
                  class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-accent mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"
